# ⚡ ByteDrop

> 🚀 Instant file sharing between your devices — no internet required.

---

## 🌌 What is ByteDrop?

**ByteDrop** is a lightweight, blazing-fast file transfer tool that lets you send files between your laptop and phone instantly over the same network.

No cloud. No login. No nonsense.

Just **drag → drop → download**.

---

## ✨ Features

* ⚡ **Instant Transfer** — No delays, no uploads to internet
* 🌐 **Works Offline** — Same WiFi is enough
* 📱 **QR Code Connect** — No typing IPs
* 🖱️ **Drag & Drop Anywhere** — Drop files from anywhere on screen
* ❌ **Delete Files Anytime** — Full control over uploads
* 🌙 **Dark Mode UI** — Clean, minimal design
* 💻 **Lightweight** — Runs smoothly even on low-end systems

---

## 🧠 How it Works

1. Start the server on your laptop
2. Open the app in browser
3. Scan the QR code using your phone
4. Drop files → instantly available on your phone

