## ⚙️ Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR-USERNAME/byte-drop.git
cd byte-drop
npm install
node server.js
```

---

## 📱 Usage

* Open:

```
http://localhost:3000
```

* Or scan the QR code from your phone

* Drag & drop files anywhere on screen

* Click to download on your phone

---

## 🔐 Privacy

* ❌ No cloud storage
* ❌ No third-party servers
* ✅ Everything stays on your local network

---

## 🧩 Tech Stack

* Node.js
* Express
* Multer
* Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS

